Class DataDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • DataDefinition

  • public class DataDefinition
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that defines a definition for a data type be categorizing it into different variable types, allows you to construct a DataDefinition, Retrieve the description, the unit type, the variable id, the variable name, whether the data is positive or negative in value, and represent the data in a String.
    Version:
    10/17/2016
    Author:
    Kyle Roller, Nigell Mansell
